title: Converse #PeepShow | Official Video featuring Jaurim, Aziatix and Idiotape
description: Check out the official music video for #PeepShow, the first ever Korea-based 3 Artists. 1 Song collaboration featuring Jaurim, Aziatix and Idiotape. #PeepShow is a cross-pollination of three distinct music genres, weaving together Aziatix's signature rap lyrics with Jaurim's indie vocals and Idiotape's electronic sound. To find out more information and download the free track, visit: http://bit.ly/K8KXPK
